{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_04_01",
  "title": "サニーピース 04 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、遙子ちゃん\nおはようございます、二人で何をしてるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ Haruko-chan\nGood morning‚ what are you two doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.7666665792,
      "endTime": 8.3376642942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、おはよう\n遙子さんが持ってきた写真を見ていたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ good morning\nI was looking at the photos Haruko-san brought",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4909976403,
      "endTime": 13.2580496232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "部屋を片付けていたら懐かしい写真が出てきたから\n事務所に飾ってもらおうと思って持ってきたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was cleaning my room and found some nostalgic photos\nI brought them to decorate my office",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4513828516,
      "endTime": 21.1317682505,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7880.385208200001,
          "startTime": 21.3317680598
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "これ……星見市の事務所で撮った写真ですか？\n三枝さんと遙子ちゃんしか写ってないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This… is it a photo taken at the Hoshimi City office?\nOnly Saegusa-san and Haruko-chan are in the picture…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3317680598,
      "endTime": 31.0760307551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんが星見プロを立ち上げて間もない頃の写真よ\nこの頃は所属アイドルが私一人しかいなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This photo was taken shortly after Saegusa-san launched Hoshimi Prods.\nAt that time‚ I was the only idol in the office",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1626976889,
      "endTime": 40.2916094702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんはデビュー前で、まだ中学生だったんですよね\n制服姿が初々しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before Haruko-san debuted‚ she was still in middle school\nYour school uniform looks refreshing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4782762131,
      "endTime": 47.4407270034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "あら、私は今でも制服が似合うピチピチの十七歳よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm still a young 17 years old who looks good in a school uniform",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6407269081,
      "endTime": 54.2607041916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ、そうですね……今時の十七歳は\nピチピチなんて言わない気もしますが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Well‚ that's right… I don't think\npeople who are actually 17 years old would say they are young…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.4740374964,
      "endTime": 61.6552392404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "中学生かあ……そんな頃から事務所に所属してたなんて\n遙子ちゃんは凄いなあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Middle school… working at the office from that age\nHaruko-chan is so amazing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8685724021,
      "endTime": 70.60773370279999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、ちゃんと聞いたことなかったけど\n遙子ちゃんはどうしてアイドルになろうと思ったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I've never heard of it\nWhy did you want to become an idol‚ Haruko-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7944005412,
      "endTime": 78.1644231242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "大した話じゃないわ。みんなと同じように\nアイドルを好きになって、アイドルに憧れただけよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not an unusual stroy. Just like everyone else‚\nI like idols‚ and admire them",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.3644229335,
      "endTime": 87.00610059930001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10128.344217900009,
          "startTime": 88.4927671514
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.2427671514
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.2427671514
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.4927671514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "（私が初めて生でアイドルを見たのは）\n（第一回NEXT VENUSグランプリの会場だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The first time I saw idols live）\n（It was at the venue of the first NEXT VENUS Grand Prix）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2927671514,
      "endTime": 96.4787987791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "（両親に連れられて訪れた会場で、幼い私は）\n（目の前で光り輝くアイドル達に夢中になった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（My parents took me to the venue‚ and young girl）\n（was obsessed with the idols who shone brightly in front of her）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.9188106301,
      "endTime": 105.4000071208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "（頑張れば私もあんな風に輝けるのかな、私も）\n（あんな風にキラキラ輝きたいな……って、そう思った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If I try hard‚ I can shine like that‚）\n（I want to shine like that… that's what I thought）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7395113073,
      "endTime": 115.40309296470001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.7395113073
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.5497593644
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.7830926977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "（そうしてアイドルのライブに夢中になった私は……）\n（気付くと両親とはぐれていて、会場で迷子になった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And I was so obsessed with idol's live…）\n（When I came to‚ I was separated from my parents and lost in the venue）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6497588558,
      "endTime": 125.3861525936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.7194838924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "ぐすっ……お父さん、お母さん……どこ……？\nどこにいるの……疲れてもう歩けないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sniff… Dad‚ Mom… Where are you…?\nWhere are you… I'm so tired I can't walk anymore…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.7194838924,
      "endTime": 138.6378510875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "足痛いよ……動けないよ……もう無理だよ……\nこのままもう会えないのかな、おうちに帰れないのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My legs hurt… I can't move… I can't do this anymore…\nWill I never see you again‚ will I never be able to go home?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.8978498222,
      "endTime": 155.67694337380001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14597.093518500003,
          "startTime": 153.4949433407
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.8702766499
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hoshimura001.m4a",
      "text": "お嬢ちゃん、泣いちゃダメよ、諦めちゃダメよ\n私が一緒に探してあげるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't cry‚ little girl‚ don't give up\nI'll help you find your parents",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8702766499,
      "endTime": 162.963617333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "（迷子になった私は、そこで、とても優しくて）\n（とても綺麗なお姉さんに保護されたの）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I became lost and was protected by）\n（a very kind and beautiful older sister there）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.1702837708,
      "endTime": 170.6928007842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.1702837708
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.84
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "館内アナウンス",
      "speakerNameEn": "PA",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-knana001.m4a",
      "text": "迷子のお知らせをいたします、星見市からお越しの\n佐伯遙子ちゃんの保護者の方は、一階受付まで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're announcing a lost child‚ Parents of Haruko Saeki\nfrom Hoshimi City‚ Please come to the reception on the first floor――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.9861247143,
      "endTime": 181.83332824709998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.1528056225
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hoshimura002.m4a",
      "text": "迷子のアナウンスを流したから、これで大丈夫よ\nすぐにお父さんとお母さんが迎えに来てくれるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've made an announcement‚ so you'll be fine\nYour parents will come and pick you up soon",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.08613743,
      "endTime": 191.479471628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "うん……ありがとう……\n……もしかして、お姉さんはアイドルなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… thank you…\n…One-san‚ are you idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.6861384472,
      "endTime": 199.6328059276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_01-hoshimura003.m4a",
      "text": "あら、どうしてそう思うの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ why do you think so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.8261391085,
      "endTime": 202.2794674081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
