      "text": "ふふ、ありがとう。私は元アイドルよ\n今はアイドルを引退して裏方をしているの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ thank you. I'm a former idol\nI've retired from idol now and work behind the scenes",
        "id": ""
